  "time_ut": 1658399451,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dba\u0dd1\u0db8\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 33\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "33 people who tried to go to the country by boat were arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Navy conducted a special search operation in the sea area off Negombo this morning (21st) to arrest 33 people suspected of trying to illegally migrate from Sri Lanka to a foreign country by sea.",
        "The P 435 fast attack craft belonging to the fourth fast attack craft squadron attached to the Western Naval Command today (21st) during a search operation carried out in the sea area off Migomu observed and inspected a suspected multi-day fishing vessel.",
        "There, 33 persons, including four crew members of the multi-day fishing vessel, who were suspected of attempting to illegally migrate from the country to a foreign country by sea, were taken into custody by the navy.",
        "In this search operation, the people who were taken into custody by the navy and the people between the ages of 18 and 65 were identified as residents of Halawata, Marawila, Trincomalee, Batticaloa and Ampara, and the group is to be handed over to the Colombo Port Police for further investigations. have."
      ],
